{"type": "article", "id": 26920, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-05-17T06:45:50Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 27710, "name": "Tree Bag"}, {"id": 27711, "name": "Waltz"}, {"id": 27712, "name": "GamFratesi"}, {"id": 27713, "name": "Harry Allen Esque"}, {"id": 27714, "name": "Teplo"}, {"id": 27715, "name": "Moss Clock"}, {"id": 27716, "name": "Acanvas"}, {"id": 27717, "name": "reWrap"}, {"id": 27650, "name": "Oscar Diaz Studio"}, {"id": 27718, "name": "Load&Road LLC"}, {"id": 27719, "name": "Paul Noktuku"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702152810BtUiHKZayWfeqjxX.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>          </p>\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>Tree Bag by reWrap</h2>\n<p>为了应对环境污染，你或许已经见识过各种可降解的物品，来自德国的年轻品牌 <a href=\"http://www.rewrap.eu/\">reWrap</a> 想让你的日常用品也能带有环保属性，推出了这款用可降解材料制成的公文包。这个棕色的公文包主体由椰子纤维压制而成，缝线部分则使用了木浆。天然的材料以及简约的设计，看上去充满了大自然的气息。如果你感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"http://www.rewrap.eu/shop/tree-bag-large/\">链接</a>购买到这款足够环保的公文包，售价为 275 欧元（包含邮费）。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111115lnr1RATF0UQeIMBy.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71882641\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111116QUhoXiDVgJCmr05f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58190709\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111116WjvedHxbc9SE2FTA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111117LaGwN2v8d0rtE9ST.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111117NLl3XVsBb6Sp2meu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021111174FhaJiK1mCUIfMlc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Waltz by GamFratesi</h2>\n<p>千篇一律的衣架造型是不是已经让你感到厌烦了？丹麦设计双人组 GamFratesi 以舞者的动作为灵感，设计了一款名为 Waltz 的衣架系统。它其实是由多个模块拼接而成，你可以根据需要将它们延长或者缩短。朝上的圆弧很适合挂上大衣，你也可以在朝下的圆弧中放上围巾或者挂上一把伞。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111118Wwq49HTePFrbUOk2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.83974359\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111119WZQqPYr0yKEOVa5F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111119sqFPWoXEyZUjVmR2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111120ZBphJ48AFDqi5vOy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Harry Allen Esque by Oscar Diaz Studio</h2>\n<p>这组漂亮的灯具是纽约设计师 <a href=\"http://www.harryallendesign.com/home.htm\">Harry Allen</a> 和波特兰玻璃工作室 <a href=\"http://esque-studio.com/\">Esque Studio</a> 第二次合作的产物。每一件均由手工吹制的玻璃和水刀切割的金属片组合而成，制作过程中的差异最终也反应在了独一无二的成品上，看起来很像是宇宙中造型各异的星球。Harry Allen Esque 灯具系列目前正在纽约的 <a href=\"http://www.hellergallery.com/\">Heller Gallery</a> 进行展出，展览将持续到 5 月 28 日。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021111200BCWRQV4sSw7ElMA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76528117\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111121g3FozTUwvkWiX91Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111121og8rLsc9FMnvE2R3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.91442543\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111122GKoBknORbdVIwWFm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.84841076\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111122SW7sv3AljikDn95E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64547677\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111123FJAYZrEM8u0Sg5Pn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.09168704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Teplo by Load&amp;Road LLC</h2>\n<p>Load&amp;Road LLC 的创始人们来自日本和印度这两个有着浓厚的茶文化的国家，深知泡一杯好茶不是件容易事，于是他们决定为爱茶人士设计一款可以指示你该如何泡茶的智能茶杯。这个名为 Teplo 的茶杯有一个配套手机应用，根据你所选择的茶叶类型，它会提醒你沏茶、取出茶叶的时机。除此之外，一旦到达可以饮用的温度，Teplo 还可以提供 4 小时的保温。如果你对这种智能泡茶的体验感兴趣，可以通过<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/teplo-the-1st-smart-bottle-for-tea-lovers#/\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 44 美元。 </p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111123jbgJYsi9PdKNuB6L.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56290323\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111124Kdwayp6G1ZPFkruI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55806452\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111124Z4snP8ictKjg0QNf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55645161\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111125Q0JhxqTdfLRFDbHP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56290323\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070211112523iXA1scaf9t0Gwp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56290323\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111126D634wrkLgiB7Pb81.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56290323\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Moss Clock by Paul Noktuku</h2>\n<p>打算给家里增添一点绿意可以从很多小地方做起，一个以苔藓作钟面的挂钟就是一个不错的选择。设计师 Paul Noktuku 选用挪威的驯鹿苔藓作为材料，大约每 2 千克的生苔藓才能制作一款挂钟，由于经过处理，你也无需为它们浇水。Noktuku 根据颜色还形象地将它们分别命名为夏、秋、冬三款。目前正在 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/mossclock/the-moss-clock\">Kickstarter</a> 上进行众筹，夏和秋款的价格为 300 欧元，冬款为 320 欧元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111126s6orAdxZpfL2uaz1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111126hNR3L61z7cG5d0up.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.99411765\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021111279hw3ujfI8WsJnlqO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111127I9PDWuZjRpxqNMkf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.12647059\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111128lTPzShsjG1O7Vgxo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.99264706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021111287v1LUCAFrVdgQezq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.22352941\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Acanvas by Acanvas</h2>\n<p>要感谢不止提供视频和音乐的流媒体服务，你现在可以拥有一件会动的艺术品了：这个名为 Acanvas 的智能画框与一个艺术作品库相连，通过配套的手机应用你可以挑选自己喜欢的作品显示在“画布”上。Acanvas 另一个非常智能的设计在于它可以根据光线明暗在黑暗时自动降下连接线为自己充电，你可以根据需要将它和充电器放在家里的任何地方。你可以通过链接参与 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/acanvas/acanvas-the-cord-free-art-display-and-streaming-pl\">Acanvas</a> 的众筹，早鸟价为 299 美元（包含了艺术库的一年 120 美元的订阅费）。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111129XMUamH5l2L9BOoGc.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.59117647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111129e0hXpr6754lKLGMk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59117647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021111303sezDdG49a2ipXVJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69411765\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021111307JF4YGb2MQjDB5Zz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.01764706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111130RAPYniz8NXqQW7UO.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111132SCayQb1Zokgz7mqh.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}